PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
SELECT DISTINCT ?uri
WHERE {

        ?uri dbp:officialLanguages ituage .
} 
ORDER BY DESC(COUNT(ituage)) 
OFFSET 0 LIMIT 1

question: Which bridges are of the same type as the Manhattan Bridge?
sparql:
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>
PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
SELECT DISTINCT ?uri
WHERE {       
        ?uri rdf:type dbo:Bridge .
        ?uri dbp:design ?design .
        res:Manhattan_Bridge dbp:design ?mdesign . 
        FILTER (?design = ?mdesign && ?uri != res:Manhattan_Bridge) . 
}
